text: Hartland Community School is a K-12 school located in Hartland, New Brunswick, Canada. Hartland Community School has around 575 students.Hartland Community School The students in Hartland Community School are from all of Carleton County. ==See also== * List of schools in New Brunswick * Anglophone West School District ==References== Category:Schools in Carleton County, New Brunswick Category:High schools in New Brunswick Category:Elementary schools in New Brunswick Category:Middle schools in New Brunswick
